      "span_text": "Then, we use a standard Maximum-likelihood HMM model trained on L1 English speech (from the TIMIT corpus) with 39 dimensional PLP features [CITATION_1] to generate recognized transcriptions, and apply them both in training and testing based on the linear regression model (see Section 4.2)."
